Interface PersistentStore

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject.EStore
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDirectWriteStore, AbstractPersistentStore, AbstractPersistentStoreDecorator, AutocommitStoreDecorator, DirectWriteBlueprintsCacheManyStore, DirectWriteBlueprintsStore, DirectWriteHBaseStore, DirectWriteMapCacheManyStore, DirectWriteMapIndicesStore, DirectWriteMapListsStore, DirectWriteMapStore, FeatureCachingStoreDecorator, InvalidStore, IsSetCachingStoreDecorator, LoadedObjectCounterStoreDecorator, LoggingStoreDecorator, ReadOnlyHBaseStore, SizeCachingStoreDecorator

    public interface PersistentStore
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject.EStore
    This interface extends the InternalEObject.EStore interface and allows to establish a mapping between Resources and InternalEObject.EStores.
